trans-unit.source: Represents a control that allows the user to select a date.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en kontroll som tillater at brukeren velger en dato.

trans-unit.source: The DatePicker control allows the user to select a date by either typing it into a text field or by using a drop-down <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Calendar> control.
trans-unit.target: Kontrollen DatePicker lar brukeren velger en dato ved enten å skrive det inn i et tekstfelt eller en rullegardinliste <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Calendar>kontroll.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Calendar>

trans-unit.source: Many of a DatePicker control's properties are for managing its built-in <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Calendar>, and function identically to the equivalent property in <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Calendar>.
trans-unit.target: Mange av egenskapene for en DatePicker kontroll er for behandling av innebygde <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Calendar>, og funksjonen identisk med den tilsvarende egenskapen i <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Calendar>.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Calendar> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Calendar>

trans-unit.source: In particular, the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DatePicker.IsTodayHighlighted%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DatePicker.FirstDayOfWeek%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DatePicker.BlackoutDates%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DatePicker.DisplayDateStart%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DatePicker.DisplayDateEnd%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DatePicker.DisplayDate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, and <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DatePicker.SelectedDate%2A?displayProperty=fullName> properties function identically to their <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Calendar> counterparts.
trans-unit.target: Spesielt den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DatePicker.IsTodayHighlighted%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DatePicker.FirstDayOfWeek%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DatePicker.BlackoutDates%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DatePicker.DisplayDateStart%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DatePicker.DisplayDateEnd%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DatePicker.DisplayDate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, og <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DatePicker.SelectedDate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>Egenskaper funksjonen identisk til sine <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Calendar>kolleger.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Calendar> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.DatePicker.SelectedDate%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.DatePicker.DisplayDate%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.DatePicker.DisplayDateEnd%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.DatePicker.DisplayDateStart%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.DatePicker.BlackoutDates%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.DatePicker.FirstDayOfWeek%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.DatePicker.IsTodayHighlighted%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: For more information, see <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Calendar>.
trans-unit.target: For mer informasjon, kan du se <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Calendar>.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Calendar>

trans-unit.source: Users can type a date directly into a text field, which sets the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DatePicker.Text%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Brukere kan skrive en dato direkte i et felt for tekst, som angir den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DatePicker.Text%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.DatePicker.Text%2A>

trans-unit.source: If the DatePicker cannot convert the entered string to a valid date, the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DatePicker.DateValidationError> event will be raised.
trans-unit.target: Hvis datovelgeren ikke kan konvertere den angitte strengen til en gyldig dato i <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DatePicker.DateValidationError>hendelsen vil opp.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.DatePicker.DateValidationError>

trans-unit.source: By default, this causes an exception, but an event handler for <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DatePicker.DateValidationError> can set the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DatePickerDateValidationErrorEventArgs.ThrowException%2A> property to `false` and prevent an exception from being raised.
trans-unit.target: Som standard, ettersom dette skaper et unntak, men en hendelsesbehandling for <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DatePicker.DateValidationError>kan angi den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DatePickerDateValidationErrorEventArgs.ThrowException%2A>egenskapen `false` og hindre et unntak fra blir opphøyd.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.DatePickerDateValidationErrorEventArgs.ThrowException%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.DatePicker.DateValidationError>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > The DatePicker supports only the Gregorian calendar.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > For DatePicker støtter bare gregoriansk kalender.

trans-unit.source: Customizing the DatePicker Control To apply the same property settings to multiple DatePicker controls, use the <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.Style%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Tilpasse DatePicker kontrollen til i gjelder samme egenskapsinnstillingene flere DatePicker kontroller, bruk av <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.Style%2A>egenskap.</xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.Style%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can modify the default <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ControlTemplate> to give the control a unique appearance.
trans-unit.target: Du kan endre standard <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ControlTemplate>Gi kontrollen unikt utseende.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ControlTemplate>

trans-unit.source: For more information about creating a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ControlTemplate>, see [Customizing the Appearance of an Existing Control by Creating a ControlTemplate](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: For mer informasjon om hvordan du oppretter en <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ControlTemplate>, se [tilpasse utseendet til en eksisterende kontroll ved å opprette en ControlTemplate](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ControlTemplate>

trans-unit.source: To see the parts and states that are specific to the DatePicker, see [DatePicker Syles and Templates](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil se delene og statusene som er spesifikke for datovelgeren, kan du se [DatePicker Syles og maler](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: Dependency properties for this control might be set by the control’s default style.
trans-unit.target: Avhengighet egenskapene for denne kontrollen, kan angis ved kontrollens standardstilen.

trans-unit.source: If a property is set by a default style, the property might change from its default value when the control appears in the application.
trans-unit.target: Hvis en egenskap er satt av en standardstilen, kan endre egenskapen standardverdi når kontrollen vises i applikasjonen.

trans-unit.source: The default style is determined by which desktop theme is used when the application is running.
trans-unit.target: Standardstilen er avhengig av hvilken stasjonær tema brukes når programmet kjører.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Default WPF Themes](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=158252).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, se [standard WPF oppsett](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=158252).

trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Angi en visual egenskap trenger bare en effekt hvis egenskapen er begge finnes i standardmal for knappekontrollen og angis ved hjelp av en.

trans-unit.source: You can find a list of visual properties in the "Changing the Visual Structure of a Control" section in [Customizing the Appearance of an Existing Control by Creating a ControlTemplate](../Topic/Customizing%20the%20Appearance%20of%20an%20Existing%20Control%20by%20Creating%20a%20ControlTemplate.md).

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DatePicker> attempts to parse any string entered into this property as a date.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DatePicker>prøver å analysere en streng som er angitt i egenskapen som en dato.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.DatePicker>

trans-unit.source: While the Text property can be set to any string that can be parsed by the <xref:System.DateTime.Parse%2A> method date, the format of the string that is returned depends on the value of the <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo.CurrentCulture%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property.
trans-unit.target: Under Text-egenskapen kan settes til en streng som kan bli analysert av den <xref:System.DateTime.Parse%2A>metoden dato formatet for strengen som returneres er avhengig av verdien for den <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo.CurrentCulture%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskap.</xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo.CurrentCulture%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.DateTime.Parse%2A>

trans-unit.source: This means that the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DatePicker> might display a string that is different than what the user typed.
trans-unit.target: Dette betyr at den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DatePicker>kan vise en streng som er forskjellig fra det brukeren skrev inn.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.DatePicker>

trans-unit.source: If Text is set to a date that is selectable and valid, the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DatePicker.DateValidationError> event occurs.
trans-unit.target: Hvis teksten er satt til en dato som kan velges og gyldig den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DatePicker.DateValidationError>inntreffer.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.DatePicker.DateValidationError>

trans-unit.source: If you handle the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DatePicker.DateValidationError> event and set the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DatePickerDateValidationErrorEventArgs.ThrowException%2A> property to `true`, a <xref:System.FormatException> or <xref:System.ArgumentOutOfRangeException> is raised.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du håndtere den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DatePicker.DateValidationError>hendelsen og angitt av <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DatePickerDateValidationErrorEventArgs.ThrowException%2A>egenskapen `true`, en <xref:System.FormatException>eller <xref:System.ArgumentOutOfRangeException>oppstår.</xref:System.ArgumentOutOfRangeException> </xref:System.FormatException> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.DatePickerDateValidationErrorEventArgs.ThrowException%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.DatePicker.DateValidationError>
